se.ltu.android.demo.scene
Class PieceData

java.lang.Object
  se.ltu.android.demo.scene.PieceData

public class PieceData
extends java.lang.Object

An application specific data object to be set on a spatial's setData-method. This object holds information about chess pieces placement on the board and the color of the piece.
